WEBVTT

00:03:59.005 --> 00:04:00.615
saya akan tunjukkan kemahiran saya.

00:04:00.615 --> 00:04:01.350
Saya akan kata,

00:04:01.350 --> 00:04:02.563
"Apa khabar?"

00:04:02.563 --> 00:04:03.548
"Apa cerita?"

00:04:03.548 --> 00:04:06.452
Dan semestinya, "Helo."

00:04:06.452 --> 00:04:09.126
Sebab, saya "ada bakat dalam bahasa".

00:04:09.126 --> 00:04:11.439
Terima kasih. (Tepukan)